{"tid":911633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［外星科技］有無人識得燒傷面個位女仔或者家人？","createTime":"2018-11-22T05:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T14:18:52.000Z","uid":40250,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"637a82fe4b408182600858d2839e3d6019ffe627","tid":911633,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://medkit.info/2018/08/23/avita-medical-clinical-trial-results-demonstrate-safety-efficacy-of-recell-device-in-treating-burn-patients/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedkit.info%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2Favita-medical-clinical-trial-results-demonstrate-safety-efficacy-of-recell-device-in-treating-burn-patients%2F&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPMwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=80a89862\" target=\"_blank\">https://medkit.info/2018/08/23/avita-medical-clinical-trial-results-demonstrate-safety-efficacy-of-recell-device-in-treating-burn-patients/</a><br />\n<br />\n兩年前八仙塵爆，講緊有種新既stem cell spray gun去治療重度燒傷, 個陣連clinical trial都未有，所以都係得個講字。<br />\n<br />\n兩年後，renovacare未成功囉到FDA approval, 但係Avita既Recell system已經係今年9月囉到FDA premarket approval, 亦有美軍都試用過，效果理想。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.biospace.com/article/releases/avita-medical-announces-government-funded-clinical-trial-of-recell-in-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biospace.com%2Farticle%2Freleases%2Favita-medical-announces-government-funded-clinical-trial-of-recell-in-china%2F&d=dfeeB01biWcpSatpjJUPMwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5c49b736\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.biospace.com/article/releases/avita-medical-announces-government-funded-clinical-trial-of-recell-in-china/</a><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，Avita 都帶clinical trial係中國進行，都係幫軍方醫院試。<br />\n<br />\n二至三級燒傷，唔係期望conventional healing可以幫到你，機會就眼前，幫唔幫到自己就睇你有幾大決心"},{"pid":"46289f5e9af00340afb10631ffd466b464572e6b","tid":911633,"uid":156363,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"叫侵大班醫生醫返佢地啦。"},{"pid":"31e26